txt.en: Ingold can be found at the northern gate of the Rammas.\n\nYou should speak with Ingold.
'You have accomplished much. You say you have defeated their captain as well? Then the North-gate remains ours, [placeholder]!'
Jal Vârsha can be found along the northern Rammas in southern Talath Anor.\n\nYou should defeat Sûhalar guards and their captain.

'I am worried about the Sûhalar encampment against the northern Rammas. Its numbers continue to grow. I fear they may try to take the Rammas and the North-gate if left unchecked.\n\n'I'm counting on you to defeat the forces gathered there. Be careful, as the axe-men are strong and skilled warriors.'
The Sûhalar Easterlings have constructed an encampment at the base of the northern Rammas. Ingold worries that they may try to attack the North-gate if their growing numbers are not handled.
